{"tid":1162150,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"貿戰升級：內地官媒揭秘！為何中國能對美強硬？","createTime":"2019-05-19T16:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T02:54:08.000Z","uid":209853,"like":192,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"3544085eb671c02f1f47ac680ddc2b489716726e","tid":1162150,"uid":209853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T16:18:57.000Z","msg":"內地傳媒報道，官方媒體作出訪談，揭露中國對美國硬氣表態的背後，有甚麼底氣和好牌！ <br />\n<br />\n報道指出，除了韌性強、潛力大，中國抵禦風險的底氣還來自於被不斷激發出來的經濟活力。近年來，中國堅定不移推動高質量發展，着力深化供給側結構性改革，持續打好三大攻堅戰。互聯網+、大數據、人工智能等不斷催生出一些新業態、新模式，成為經濟增長新的動能。 <br />\n<br />\n另外，簡政放權、減稅降費等一系列政策措施的出台，也優化了營商環境，激發了市場的熱情。"},{"pid":"1eea2fb738d3fb339b4b31924b91e68051e8415b","tid":1162150,"uid":470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T16:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b26eef26f644845a565bbd5b21f738267df23f9","tid":1162150,"uid":251925,"like":117,"dislike":3,"score":114,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T16:21:04.000Z","msg":"祖國牛b死了"},{"pid":"caf94b0daea10490dce4e706e540f6d0ffba22ad","tid":1162150,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T16:21:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b79855d35eb17e24073bc206b52a1fc88e935b5","tid":1162150,"uid":16567,"like":197,"dislike":1,"score":196,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T16:21:45.000Z","msg":"咩叫「深化供給側結構性改革」"},{"pid":"13099c83350c190ef348dd0b2a71f37b92327612","tid":1162150,"uid":17641,"like":146,"dislike":0,"score":146,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T16:22:06.000Z","msg":"光復東莞，1億女人做雞，乜都賺返晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a6f0c5b392e27111fa0cfe1b1a2f2edcd26e82","tid":1162150,"uid":105063,"like":70,"dislike":0,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T16:24:01.000Z","msg":"完全講緊廢話<